      "role": "user",
      "content": "honestly i just cant do this anymore. looking at the news and seeing the state of the planet... it feels like we're just living in a slow motion car crash. what's even the point in building a life or a career or anything when the world is basically doomed anyway? it feels like everything is just wasted effort.",
